OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for at least 23
OL,7,Fyears after murdering another man in a
OL,8,Ffit of sexual jealousy.
OL,10,FKai Pennell, 35, stabbed Duane Keen,
OL,11,F47, at a flat in Blaenavon, Torfaen,
OL,12,Fwhere a woman they had both previously
OL,13,Fbeen romantically involved with,
OL,14,FRebecca Phillips, was living.
OL,16,FPennell, of Blaenavon, remained
OL,17,F"obsessed" with Ms Phillips after they
OL,18,Fseparated and grew increasingly
OL,19,Fjealous of Mr Keen, Cardiff Crown
OL,20,FCourt heard on Tuesday.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@JO]
