OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,FHe stabbed Mr Keen in the chest after
OL,7,Fforcing entry to the flat in the early
OL,8,Fhours of the morning of October 17
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FMrs Justice Stacey said: "You appeared
OL,12,Funable to accept that she did not want
OL,13,Fto be in a relationship with you. You
OL,14,Fwould not leave her alone and you
OL,15,Fbecame fixated on whether she was
OL,16,Fseeing anyone else, including her ex,
OL,17,FDuane Keen."
OL,26,@sD@ZOUyD@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
