OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,FCardiff Crown Court heard Pennell was
OL,7,Fa former partner of Ms Phillips but
OL,8,Fshe had ended their romantic
OL,9,Finvolvement in September 2025.
OL,11,FMr Keen was also a former partner of
OL,12,FMs Phillips, although the pair had
OL,13,Fseparated in May that year.
OL,15,FChristopher Rees KC, prosecuting,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The prosecution case is that
OL,17,F(Pennell) remained obsessed with her
OL,18,Fand burning with jealousy. Kai Pennell
OL,19,Fwas motivated by sexual jealousy to
OL,20,Fmurder Duane Keen."
OL,26,@xD@GOU|D@SO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
