OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,FOn the night of the murder, Pennell
OL,7,Fhad bombarded Ms Phillips with
OL,8,F"disturbing" calls and text messages,
OL,9,Fthe court heard.
OL,11,FFeeling unsafe, she asked Mr Keen to
OL,12,Fcome to her address, where they were
OL,13,Fboth ambushed by Pennell, who forced
OL,14,Fhis way into the property and stabbed
OL,15,FMr Keen in the chest.
OL,17,FHe fled the scene but was located by
OL,18,Fpolice later that morning.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
