OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, 24 February, Mrs Justice
OL,7,FStacey issued a life sentence to
OL,8,FPennell, with a minimum custodial term
OL,9,Fof 23 years, and imposed an indefinite
OL,10,Frestraining order prohibiting him from
OL,11,Fcontacting Ms Phillips.
OL,13,FHe will serve a minimum of 22 years
OL,14,Fand 138 days in prison, due to time
OL,15,Falready spent in custody.
OL,17,FShe said: "In your twisted and self-
OL,18,Fpiteous logic you told her that your
OL,19,Fmurder of Duane was somehow her fault.
OL,20,FThe only person to blame for Duane's
OL,21,Fmurder is you.
OL,26,@yD@KOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,F"You were motivated by sexual jealousy
OL,7,Fand anger when you killed Duane and as
OL,8,Fa way to try and control and punish
OL,9,FRebecca for breaking up with you and
OL,10,Fremaining friends with Duane."
OL,12,FMr Keen was described in court as
OL,13,Fbeing "well-known" in the mixed
OL,14,Fmartial arts (MMA) community but
OL,15,F"first and foremost a family man".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]uD@GOUuD@RO]wD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
