FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,FIn a statement, his family said:
OL,7,F"Although justice has been given, the
OL,8,Flife sentence will never be truly
OL,9,Fenough, as we the family have lost our
OL,10,Floved one who will never have his life
OL,11,Fto live and we now have to live the
OL,12,Frest of our lives without him.
OL,14,F"We the family would like to thank the
OL,15,Fpolice, CPS and all the team that have
OL,16,Fworked tirelessly on this case and
OL,17,Fhave supported us throughout the past
OL,18,Fseveral months."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
