OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Jitka
OL,7,FTomkova-Griffiths, of Gwent Police,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Kai Pennell killed Duane Keen
OL,9,Fin a jealousy-fuelled and violent
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,F"Taking a knife from his own property
OL,13,Fimplied that he intended to cause
OL,14,Fserious harm when confronting Duane in
OL,15,Fthe early hours of that morning.
OL,17,F"His actions had devastating
OL,18,Fconsequences and Duane's death has
OL,19,Fimpacted the lives of his family,
OL,20,Floved ones, friends and community.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
