OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1771963515
OL,3,CMan jailed after committing murder in
OL,4,Cfit of sexual jealousy
OL,6,F"I'd like to pay tribute to the
OL,7,Ffriends and family who have had to
OL,8,Fcome to terms with Duane's death and
OL,9,Fshown great strength throughout this
OL,10,Fdifficult process.
OL,12,F"I know today's sentencing will never
OL,13,Fbring him back. However, I hope this
OL,14,Foutcome brings some consolation and
OL,15,Fclosure for them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@RO]
